<div  style="text-align: center;margin-left:50px ;">
    <h1 style="text-align: center;justify-self: center;">About <i>NEXA</i></h1>
<p style='width:400px;text-align: center;'>
    Welcome to <i> <b>NEXA</b> </i> , a dynamic platform that encourages creativity , connection through its diverse scope of information amongst its users.Our blog creates a platform for users to share their undiluted opinions ; be it political,technological,scientific,educational,health,gaming or other varieties of categories of information diversely available on this platform.With this intuitive interface , users can create posts that resonate with lots of the many users on the app . Join the  <i>NEXA</i>  community to explore a plethora of creatively composed narratives and connect with a world of ideas that reflect the intelligent nature of users . <i><b>NEXA :- Where stories shape tomorrow. </b></i>
</p>

